items.raw_desc: Szervízkészlet Sixtol Sada na odvzdušnění brzd Mechanic Brake Bleeding set:With the practical MECHANIC BRAKE BLEEDING SET 8 you can change brake fluid at home. Brake fluid has the ability to absorb moisture in the air, lowering its boiling point and adversely changing its operating characteristics.
